}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The S/N of the hub populating this entry is '''C50'''''1749243''.
The '''[[Belkin]]''' logo and "12416 rev:1.2 /1.0mm" is silkscreened on the board. :The '''[[SMSC]]''' hub IC package is marked with "SMSC", "USB2507-ADT", "A0519-AC16", and "8R120860E". :The board is using all '''Canicon''' electrolytic capacitors and a '''Sirect Semi''' MT1117 -3.3A 0515 LDO voltage regulator.
The power adapter included with the device is a '''DEER COMPUTER''' AD1805C (100-240VAC ~ 47-63Hz, 1.0A -> 4.0-5.5V 3.8A max.).
